			<h3>Lifestyle Lens Implants</h3>
			<div>
				<p>Experience clear vision after cataract surgery at the Eye &amp; LASIK Center. Doctors Pierre R. Alfred and John F. Warren offer the most advanced intraocular (IOL) lens technology including Tecnis, ReSTOR Multifocal, and Crystalens accommodating IOLs. Traditional monofocal lens replacement provides for one improved focal point, distance, leaving people dependent on readers or bifocals after cataract surgery. Premium lens implants now make it possible to improve patients&#8217; vision at all ranges, near through distance, with increased freedom from glasses or contact lenses.<br />
